txt.en: We should dispatch with him, before he whips our enemies into a frenzy!
Defeat Okurayo the Minstrel quickly, before he heartens our foes and dispirits our men.
A Corsair minstrel has appeared in the area, shouting insults and egging on our foes.
'Might of Umbar, might of Umbar! Be avenged!'
'Here, boys! Here's some sport before we set sail northward!'
'What rats are these, skulking 'round up here?'
'Flash your blades and flex your bows! Brook no quarter to your foes!'

A Minstrel has climbed up to your vantage point, shouting insults and egging on our foes. Dispatch him before he whips your enemies into a frenzy.

This quest starts with <rgb=#FFFF00>empty</rgb> Merit Rating.

<rgb=#00FF00>Merit Gain:</rgb>
* Defeat Okurayo 
* Defeat Okurayo quickly
'And here I thought all the rats had fled the city!'
'Make them weep and make them whimper! Watch them cower, beg, and simper!'
<rgb=#FF0000>You have left Okurayo unchallenged for too long.</rgb>
